#!/usr/bin/env perl
use strict;
use warnings;
use Alien::Ditaa;

our $VERSION = '0.001';

Alien::Ditaa->run_ditaa(@ARGV);

1;

=head1 NAME

ditaa - Trivial wrapper script for ditaa.jar

=head1 SYNOPSIS

    ditaa infile.txt outfile.png

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Trivial wrapper to run ditaa.jar.

=head1 SEE ALSO

L<http://ditaa.sourceforge.net>

=head1 INCLUDED SOFTWARE

An unmodified copy of the latest varion of ditaa.jar is included in
this package. The latest version and source code can be obtained
from the URI above.

